the only country singer in the universe.

47
00:08:17,086 --> 00:08:19,020
I guess this means they're extinct.

48
00:08:19,088 --> 00:08:21,215
- And the suspect?
- I dunno.

49
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:23,224
Tell me, is that crazy getup
you're wearing...

50
00:08:23,292 --> 00:08:25,726
