on this end of town.

123
00:12:39,382 --> 00:12:42,351
Gee, a regular Park Avenue.

124
00:12:49,392 --> 00:12:51,326
Whoa!

125
00:12:56,065 --> 00:12:58,966
Twelfth floor.

126
00:12:59,035 --> 00:13:01,526
