have needed anyway.

132
00:13:20,156 --> 00:13:23,216
There's enough trash
from Earth here already.

133
00:13:23,292 --> 00:13:25,692
Well, you do have a point about that.

134
00:13:25,761 --> 00:13:28,696
Look at this.

135
00:13:32,268 --> 00:13:34,793
This is a tape sent by the suspect...

136
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:37,896
